latestPosts.caption:
GLITCH STITCH by Sathiga Jagatheesan ✨🧵
This collection is a piece of my heart — a fusion of digital chaos and delicate craftsmanship. It represents every glitch I’ve embraced and every stitch I’ve carefully placed, turning imperfections into art.

This journey was filled with sleepless nights, self-doubt, small victories, and moments of growth. It’s more than a collection — it’s a part of me.

To my amazing mentors @nikethashah mam and @benphilip2002 sir , thank you for your constant guidance, wisdom, and encouragement.

To my parents @sangeeth_jagatheesan and @jagatheesan45 and my sister @_.hakshu._ , your love, strength, and support are the reasons I could dream this big. I’m forever grateful for the way you stood by me through every step.
❤️ @shrivatshan_10 , @shrijana_03 , @_.hakshu._ , @saiharini._ thank you for being my safe space, for all the laughter, pep talks, and hugs when I needed them most.
You reminded me who I am, even in moments I felt lost.

I’m so grateful for every single person who helped bring Glitch Stitch to life.

A huge thank you team @dogm.aa , @ikriosgokul , @drushty.saruparia , @teamshazz for turning vision into reality — your hard work and dedication made every detail come alive.

To all my amazing models @aloisssthetic @selshiajuliet_ @riaaaa.sunil @subha_nandhini , thank you for bringing energy, elegance, and life to my designs.

And a very special thanks to @riaaaa.sunil , who stepped in at the last moment and truly saved the day. I couldn’t have done it without you. 💖

Glitch Stitch is not just stitched in fabric, but in love, chaos, and deep gratitude.
Thank you to everyone who helped me bring this vision to life. This is for you💗

From the mess came magic. From the glitch came the stitch. 💫
